About Us

We, the founders of G&A Invest, are a family-owned company with many visions and high ambitions. We have extensive experience in the field of construction and real estate development, bringing a comprehensive network of industry experts with us. With our profound expertise and passion for sustainable building, we aspire to transform the construction industry and bring visionary projects to life.

At ENA Residence, we welcome you to the future of living! The revolutionary new condominiums offer a life of comfort, modernity, and luxury. We provide living spaces and create work environments by investing not only in revolutionary condominiums but also in smart retail spaces, which we acquire and sell. Through targeted investments in startups in both the construction and technology sectors, GA Invest aims to give society the opportunity to grow and realize its innovative and socially relevant projects. The focus is on promoting the quality of life for people in Kosovo, incorporating both ecological and economic sustainability.

Our Mission

Welcome to the future of living! Our revolutionary new condominiums, ENA Residence, offer you a life of comfort and luxury. Equipped with Smart Home technology that automatically adjusts your apartment to your needs, you can relax and enjoy life. Our apartments are also environmentally friendly and sustainable, featuring solar energy, rainwater harvesting systems, and energy-efficient appliances. You'll love the communal spaces, including rooftop terraces, fitness studios, and community areas for events and gatherings. ENA Residence is located in emerging neighborhoods and near key transportation hubs to provide you with a convenient and modern, balanced lifestyle.

Standards of living

The life standards at ENA RESIDENCE complex are high and focused on ensuring a wonderful living experience for residents. Some of the elements that can be included are:

Design and Construction Quality:
The apartments are designed with a modern and elegant touch, utilizing the finest materials and cutting-edge construction technology to ensure a high standard of quality.

Sustainable and Eco-friendly Materials:
The commitment to the environment involves the use of sustainable and ecological materials, offering an eco-friendly alternative.

Automation and Advanced Technology:
Apartments may include automated systems and advanced technology for convenience and energy efficiency.

Security and Access Control:
High-security standards include modern security systems and access controls to ensure residents' safety and privacy.

Community and Additional Services:
Establishing a strong community with additional services, including common areas, social zones, and community activities.

Privacy and Serene Environment:
Careful design of private spaces and tranquil environments to ensure a peaceful and suitable lifestyle for residents.

Location and View:
Careful placement of the complex and providing a beautiful view with easy access to surrounding services and infrastructure.

Energy Efficiency and Cost Reduction Measures:
Investments in technology and advanced systems to increase energy efficiency and reduce daily costs.

These are just some of the aspects that may be included in the lifestyle standards at ENA RESIDENCE. Complete details can be found in official materials provided by the company and may vary depending on the building structure and services offered.

Parking Lots

ENA RESIDENCE consists of an advanced parking infrastructure, offering ample parking opportunities for its residents. With both indoor and outdoor parking, ENA RESIDENCE fulfills residents' needs for secure and permanent spaces for their vehicles.

Green Terraces

Green terraces covered with rich vegetation, creating an unparalleled and fresh environment for its residents. These terraces establish a unique connection with nature and provide a private oasis for residents to relax and enjoy the clean air. With trees, flowers, and abundant greenery, the terraces become an extension of the indoor environment and serve as excellent spaces for social gatherings, reading, or simply enjoying tranquility.

Location

ENA RESIDENCE will be built in the city of Drenas, offering a privileged location for its residents. These geographical coordinates mark a strategically positioned site at the heart of the city, allowing easy access to local infrastructure and essential services.

Sustainable and Eco-friendly Building Materials

  • Ventilated facade panels
  • Four-season glass
  • Use of ecological materials for thermal insulation
  • Utilization of soundproofing materials
  • Solar energy
  • Rainwater harvesting systems
